Direct Known Subclasses:
AggNodeMerge, ExactMatchNodeMerge, NoContentNodeMerge, ReplaceNodeMerge
abstract class NodeMerge
extends java.lang.Object

Base class for three types of node merges - 1) take the dominant content 2) do some aggregation of the content 3) exact match

Function to merge two nodes (can be attrs or elements)

Parameters:
lNode - left node to be merged
rNode - right node to be merged
resultNode - - the place to put the new result
